OL,3,CControversial 'wiggly lines' scheme to
OL,4,Cbe removed by summer 2025
OL,6,FA controversial traffic scheme which
OL,7,Fsaw wiggly lines brought to Clevedon
OL,8,Fseafront will be removed by summer
OL,9,Fnear year.
OL,11,FThe #1.3million scheme saw parking
OL,12,Fspaces facing out to sea removed, a
OL,13,F"yellow brick road" created on parts
OL,14,Fof the street and wiggly lines painted
OL,15,Fon the road.
OL,17,FResidents and visitors were quick to
OL,18,Fcriticise the changes and the RAC
OL,19,Fdescribed as one of the "most bizarre"
OL,20,Froad schemes it had seen.
