OL,6,FNorth Somerset Council is now spending
OL,7,Falmost half a million pounds to
OL,8,Freverse the changes it made to The
OL,9,FBeach in Clevedon in 2022.
OL,11,FAfter outcry in the town and an
OL,12,Findependent review of the scheme, the
OL,13,Fcouncil committed to spend #425,000
OL,14,Freversing most of the changes.
OL,16,FPeople are now being invited to a drop-
OL,17,Fin event to find out more about the
OL,18,Fchanges.
