OL,3,CControversial 'wiggly lines' scheme to
OL,4,Cbe removed by summer 2025
OL,6,FThe event will be held at Clevedon
OL,7,FCommunity Centre in Princes Road
OL,8,Fbetween 11am and 8pm on Monday 9
OL,9,FSeptember and will give people the
OL,10,Fopportunity to view new plans and talk
OL,11,Fto council officers.
