OL,3,CControversial 'wiggly lines' scheme to
OL,4,Cbe removed by summer 2025
OL,6,FHannah Young, who is the council's
OL,7,Fexecutive member with responsibility
OL,8,Ffor highways and councillor for
OL,9,FClevedon South, said: "We have
OL,10,Flistened to the community and the
OL,11,Fconsultants and we plan to reinstate
OL,12,Fthe sea facing parking, remove the two-
OL,13,Fway cycle path and adjust the
OL,14,Froundabout to a traditional layout
OL,15,Fwhich is enabled by the repositioning
OL,16,Fof the cycle lane.
