OL,3,CControversial 'wiggly lines' scheme to
OL,4,Cbe removed by summer 2025
OL,6,F"I've already had good feedback that
OL,7,Fthe new plans will address the
OL,8,Fproblems that residents and visitors
OL,9,Fhave experienced in this area and I
OL,10,Fhope the changes will make the area
OL,11,Feasier to navigate for motorists,
OL,12,Fcyclists, pedestrians and disabled
OL,13,Fusers."
OL,15,FThe changes will see the wiggly lines
OL,16,Fremoved, new loading bays and a coach
OL,17,Fdrop-off point installed as well as
OL,18,Fnew vehicular access to the Promenade
OL,19,Ffor boats and ice cream vans.
OL,20,FPedestrian crossings will be improved
OL,21,Fand planters repositioned.
