OL,4,Cbe removed by summer 2025
OL,6,FThe road will remain a one-way system
OL,7,Fbut with improved road markings and
OL,8,Fsignage. Instead of a two-way cycle
OL,9,Flane, a single contraflow cycle lane
OL,10,Fwill run alongside the road.
